---
title: Cinnamon-Apple Dutch Baby Serves 2 | with Crispy Bacon
description: This decadent Dutch baby is full of warming flavours like cinnamon, apple and maple syrup. Topped with buttery pecans, it's also served with crispy bacon for a real 'treat yourself' kind of breakfast!

Ingredients: 2% Milk (partly skimmed milk, vitamin A palmitate, vitamin D3) (milk) • Gala apple • All-purpose flour (wheat) • Grade A egg • Bacon (pork, water, salt, sugar, sodium phosphates, sodium erythorbate, sodium nitrite, spices, smoke) • Maple syrup • Pecans • Ground cinnamon.
